DESCRIPTION:
This mobile config will create shortcuts for the following network settings : 

Wifi
3G
Bluetooth
Airplane mode
GPS

This mobile config is not signed and installing this is at own risk.
There is no security policy on the mobile config so it can be deleted anytime.

INSTALLATION:
Download the Shorcuts.mobileconfig on your iPhone and install this profile.
You will see a message that this mobileconfig is unsigned but you can proceed the installation.

